%%{init: {"sequence": {"mirrorActors": false}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant UI as Time Tracker
    participant API as Time API
    participant DB as Database
    participant Analytics as Analytics

    User->>UI: Open task
    UI->>UI: Show time tracking widget

    User->>UI: Click "Start Timer"
    UI->>API: POST /api/time/start {taskId}
    API->>DB: INSERT time_entry {status: active, startedAt}
    API-->>UI: Timer running

    User->>UI: Click "Stop Timer"
    UI->>API: PATCH /api/time/{entryId}/stop
    API->>DB: UPDATE time_entry SET endedAt, duration
    API-->>UI: Logged: 2h 15m

    User->>UI: Add manual entry
    UI->>API: POST /api/time {taskId, hours, date, description}
    API->>DB: INSERT time_entry
    API-->>UI: Time logged

    UI->>API: GET /api/tasks/{id}/time-analysis
    API->>DB: Fetch task.estimatedHours
    API->>DB: SUM(time_entries.duration) as actualHours
    API->>Analytics: Calculate variance

    alt actualHours <= estimatedHours
        Analytics-->>API: Under estimate
        API-->>UI: ✓ Completed ahead of estimate
    else actualHours > estimatedHours * 1.2
        Analytics-->>API: Significantly over (>20%)
        API-->>UI: ⚠ Task took 37% longer than estimated
        API->>DB: Flag for retrospective
    else actualHours > estimatedHours
        Analytics-->>API: Slightly over
        API-->>UI: Task slightly over estimate
    end

    Manager->>UI: View team time report
    UI->>API: GET /api/reports/time?projectId=X
    API->>DB: Aggregate hours by user, task
    API-->>UI: Comparison chart (estimated vs actual)
